    'ZA' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Empowering South African Merchants with Selldone Business OS</h2>\n\n<p>Amidst the rich tapestry of cultures and landscapes in South Africa, a new e-commerce narrative is unfolding. Selldone Business OS, a no-plugin platform, is setting the stage for South African merchants to redefine their digital journey. From a myriad of products to diverse services, subscriptions, and even files, the platform offers boundless opportunities.</p>\n\n<h3>Carve Your Digital Legacy</h3>\n<p>South African businesses can now elevate their online identity. With Selldone, e-commerce seamlessly integrates into your chosen domain, fostering trust and authenticity with every interaction.</p>\n\n<h3>Effortless Digital Onboarding</h3>\n<p>Launching an online storefront in South Africa should be as vibrant and effortless as the country itself. Selldone ensures a hassle-free setup, eliminating the intricacies of hosting, plugins, and templates. It's e-commerce, simplified.</p>\n\n<h3>Harmonized with South Africa's Tax Landscape</h3>\n<p>With a deep understanding of South Africa's tax intricacies, Selldone offers integrated tax calculation features. This ensures businesses operate seamlessly, adhering to local taxation norms without complications.</p>\n\n<h3>For Brands with a Vision</h3>\n<p>From startups in Johannesburg to established brands in Cape Town, Selldone is designed to scale and evolve. It's the e-commerce partner for South African brands with ambition.</p>\n\n<h3>Optimized for Sales Mastery</h3>\n<p>Selldone is more than just a platform; it's a sales powerhouse. Designed with the South African market in mind, it's fine-tuned to convert casual browsers into loyal customers.</p>\n\n<h3>Engaging Incentives for the Rainbow Nation</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b> to celebrate and reward loyal shoppers.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b> to entice a diverse clientele.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> to elevate the shopping experience.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> for those cherished moments of appreciation.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing Tailored for South Africa</h3>\n<p>Engaging the diverse audience of South Africa is effortless with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. It's about forging connections that resonate across the nation.</p>\n\n<h3>Redefining E-commerce Standards</h3>\n<p>While platforms like WooCommerce might present challenges with hosting and a fragmented user experience, Selldone offers a cohesive and user-friendly journey for both merchants and consumers.</p>\n\n<h3>Surpassing Traditional Platforms</h3>\n<p>Conventional e-commerce platforms, such as Shopify, Salesforce, or Magento, often come with their set of challenges:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Risks</b> due to potential third-party sharing.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> that can hinder the seamless shopping experience.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> with a plethora of plugins and templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone simplifies this, offering South African merchants a streamlined, secure, and efficient e-commerce journey.</p>\n\n<p>For the visionary merchants of South Africa, Selldone Business OS is the future of e-commerce. Dive in and experience the evolution firsthand.</p>\n"],
